  <brief_title>Nasopharyngeal Packing and Rhinologic Surgery.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effectiveness of Three Different Nasopharyngeal Packing on the Prevention of Postoperative Nausea- Vomiting and Postoperative Throat Pain in Rhinologic Surgery.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Basak Ceyda MECO</agency>
