  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of three different pharyngeal packing
      during routine rhinologic surgery in the prevention of postoperative nausea and vomiting, and
      to evaluate the influence of pharyngeal packing on postoperative throat pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
